                        <persName role="scribe" corresp="PRS00000">Gäbrä Krǝstos, ʾabba</persName>According to the colophon, the scribe is ʾabba Gäbrä Krǝstos who is also the scribe of Ms. FBM-001.<date>Late 17th century</date>
